  stimulus_text = 'The museum’s newest exhibit was a great success, but one could argue that the exhibit’s title was misleading. It was called "The Art of the Americas," which, by the way, made some visitors believe the exhibit covered all the Americas. However, the exhibit was focused only on art from North America. That is, the exhibition did not include works from the Americas south of the United States.',
